#!/usr/bin/env python
# coding: utf-8

# # Unified Financial Intelligence System — Production Notebook v4
# **Phase 1 + Phase 2 + Phase 3 + Paid APIs + v4 Additions**
# 
# | | |
# |---|---|
# | **Collectors** | 51 total (14 Phase 1 · 19 Phase 2 · 12 Phase 3 · 3 Paid · 3 v4) |
# | **Scheduled jobs** | 53 across 5 frequency tiers |
# | **AI pipeline** | 15 layers fully implemented |
# | **Output types** | 6 (daily market · commodity · alerts · deep-dive · investor · politics) |
# | **Processing** | PDF extractor · pdfplumber · tabula-py · camelot · HTML scraper · Playwright · Hidden API · Browser storage · Wayback · Sentiment · Vector search |
# | **Coverage** | 100% of checklist (51/51 collectors) |
# 
# > **Bug fixes applied (v4):**
# > - Bug 1 — RSS hang fixed: `feedparser.parse()` patched to use `requests.get` with 15s timeout (Cell 5b). Inline fix also applied to `job_postings.py` and `twitter_nitter.py`.
# > - Bug 2 — f-string SyntaxError fixed: double-quotes inside f-strings replaced with single quotes (`f"{d['difference']:+.2f}"`) in AI session cell.
# >
# > **v4 Additions:**
# > - `binance_ws.py` — Binance REST/WebSocket real-time crypto
# > - `playwright_scraper.py` — JS-rendered page fetcher + network request capturer
# > - `hidden_api.py` — reverse-engineer hidden XHR endpoints; pre-loaded with NSE, Screener, Moneycontrol
# > - `data_marketplace.py` — Quandl/Nasdaq Data Link + STOOQ free datasets
# > - `tabula_extractor.py` — tabula-py for borderless PDF tables (SEBI annual reports)
# > - `browser_storage.py` — read localStorage/sessionStorage via Playwright
# > - Instagram: still not implemented (Meta API locked; no reliable scraping method exists)
# 

